# --- Wizards of the Coast IP (do not redistribute) ---
# Card art, board art, tokens, and the rulebook are copyrighted. We do NOT
# ship art with the deployed client — players' browsers fetch the source
# sheets from the original TTS Workshop mods' CDN at runtime (mod 881660322
# for base half-decks, 2745860709 for Aberrations & Undead expansion) and
# slice client-side via createImageBitmap. Local copies under assets/ are
# fine for dev/inspection but won't ship.
assets/raw/
assets/cards/
assets/board/
assets/tokens/
assets/models/
assets/site-crops/
assets/site-crops-round/
docs/rulebook.pdf

